{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_data", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "The Q1 sales reports are in. We've seen a significant increase in EV sales in the western region. I'll share the detailed report shortly.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "competitive_intelligence", "channel": "strategies", "user": "ryan_thompson", "message": "We need to keep an eye on our competitors' new EV models. I've scheduled a meeting next week to discuss this.", "created_at": 1620500030000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_data", "user": "john_smith", "message": "Noted, Jane. Looking forward to reviewing the data. I've also been doing some research on potential markets for expansion.", "created_at": 1620500060000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "competitive_intelligence", "channel": "strategies", "user": "ryan_thompson", "message": "Great point, John. We should definitely consider potential markets for our next EV model.", "created_at": 1620500090000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_data", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "I agree, expansion is key. Let's also focus on improving customer service to retain our current customers.", "created_at": 1620500120000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "competitive_intelligence", "channel": "strategies", "user": "ryan_thompson", "message": "Absolutely, Jane. Customer retention is as important as acquisition. Let's discuss this in our next meeting.", "created_at": 1620500150000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_data", "user": "john_smith", "message": "Noted, Ryan. I'll prepare some data on customer retention for our meeting.", "created_at": 1620500180000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "competitive_intelligence", "channel": "strategies", "user": "ryan_thompson", "message": "Team, as part of our efforts to maintain up-to-date personnel data, I am pleased to report that 79% of our employees have updated their ID photos this year. This is a significant increase compared to last year's update rate. Let's continue to encourage the rest to complete their updates as well.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
